trans-unit.source: Provides the methods needed to substitute one type for another by the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer> during serialization, deserialization, and export and import of XML schema documents (XSD).
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder som kreves for å erstatte én type med en annen av den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>under serialisering, deserialisering, og eksport og import av XML-skjemadokumenter (XSD).</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: Use the IDataContractSurrogate when using the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer> if you need to do one of the following: substitute one type or object for another, or to dynamically generate schema variations.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av IDataContractSurrogate ved bruk av den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>Hvis du trenger å gjøre ett av følgende: erstatte én type eller objekt for en annen, eller å generere dynamisk skjemaet variasjoner.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: For a sample application, see [DataContract Surrogate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For en programeksempelet, kan du se [DataContract erstatning](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: For more information about data contracts, see [Using Data Contracts](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om dataene kontrakter [ved hjelp av Data kontrakter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: At run time, you can find the specific <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer> for any operation in a service by using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription> to find the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.DataContractSerializerOperationBehavior> instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan finne angitt ved kjøretid, <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>for en operasjon i en tjeneste ved hjelp av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription>til å finne den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.DataContractSerializerOperationBehavior>forekomsten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.DataContractSerializerOperationBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription> </xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: For more information about implementing the interface to create a surrogate, see [Data Contract Surrogates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du implementerer grensesnittet for å opprette en erstatning [Data kontrakten surrogater](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: You can also use the IDataContractSurrogate to affect the import and export of XML schemas when you are using the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractExporter> and <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractImporter> classes.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke IDataContractSurrogate skal gjelde for import og eksport av XML-skjemaer når du bruker den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractExporter>og <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractImporter>klasser.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractImporter> </xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XsdDataContractExporter>

trans-unit.source: You can do so by assigning the IDataContractSurrogate to the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions> class, or to the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions> class.
trans-unit.target: Kan du gjøre dette ved å tilordne IDataContractSurrogate til den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A>for den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions>klassen, eller <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions>klassen.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions> </xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A> </xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions> </xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ExportOptions.DataContractSurrogate%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Schema Import and Export](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [skjemaet Importer og Eksporter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: During schema export operations, inserts annotations into the schema for non-null return values.
trans-unit.target: Setter inn merknader i skjemaet for ikke-null-returverdier under skjemaet eksportoperasjoner.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> that describes the member.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>som beskriver medlemmet.</xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the annotation to be inserted into the XML schema definition.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som representerer merknaden skal settes inn i XML-skjemadefinisjon.

trans-unit.source: During schema export operations, inserts annotations into the schema for non-null return values.
trans-unit.target: Setter inn merknader i skjemaet for ikke-null-returverdier under skjemaet eksportoperasjoner.

trans-unit.source: The CLR type to be replaced.
trans-unit.target: CLR-typen som skal erstattes.

trans-unit.source: The data contract type to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: Kontrakten datatypen til å være kommentert.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the annotation to be inserted into the XML schema definition.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som representerer merknaden skal settes inn i XML-skjemadefinisjon.

trans-unit.source: During serialization, deserialization, and schema import and export, returns a data contract type that substitutes the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Under serialisering deserialisering, og skjemaet Importer og Eksporter, returnerer kontrakten datatypen som erstatter den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: The CLR type <xref:System.Type> to substitute.
trans-unit.target: CLR-typen <xref:System.Type>skal erstatte.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The to substitute for the type value.
trans-unit.target: Den skal erstatte den type verdi.

trans-unit.source: This type must be serializable by the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen må være serialiserbare av <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: For example, it must be marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute> attribute or other mechanisms that the serializer recognizes.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den må være merket med den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>attributt eller andre mekanismer serialiseringen gjenkjenner.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>

trans-unit.source: During deserialization, returns an object that is a substitute for the specified object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som er en erstatning for det angitte objektet under deserialisering.

trans-unit.source: In a simple implementation, use an if…then…else control structure to test whether the `obj` value is of the surrogated type.
trans-unit.target: En enkel implementering Bruk en Hvis... så... Ellers kontrollere strukturen til å teste om den `obj` verdien er av typen surrogated.

trans-unit.source: If so, transform it as necessary and return the substituted object.
trans-unit.target: I så fall omgjøre dem som nødvendig og return erstattet objektet.

trans-unit.source: The substituted object can be a new instance or the same `obj` instance.
trans-unit.target: Virtuell objektet kan være en ny forekomst eller den samme `obj` forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The deserialized object to be substituted.
trans-unit.target: Deserialisert objektet som skal erstattes.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that the substituted object should be assigned to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som erstattet objektet skal tilordnes.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The substituted deserialized object.
trans-unit.target: Virtuell deserialisert objektet.

trans-unit.source: This object must be of a type that is serializable by the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: Dette objektet må være av en type som kan serialiseres av <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: For example, it must be marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute> attribute or other mechanisms that the serializer recognizes.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den må være merket med den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>attributt eller andre mekanismer serialiseringen gjenkjenner.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Sets the collection of known types to use for serialization and deserialization of the custom data objects.
trans-unit.target: Angir samlingen av kjente typer skal brukes for serialisering og deserialisering av de egendefinerte Dataobjektene.

trans-unit.source: This method is required during schema export or schema import only if annotations are inserted into the schema using the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.IDataContractSurrogate.GetCustomDataToExport%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kreves under skjemaet eksporten eller skjemaet importen bare hvis merknader settes inn i skjemaet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.IDataContractSurrogate.GetCustomDataToExport%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.IDataContractSurrogate.GetCustomDataToExport%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601> of <xref:System.Type> to add known types to.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601> for <xref:System.Type>å legge til kjente typer til.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: During serialization, returns an object that substitutes the specified object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som erstatter det angitte objektet under serialisering.

trans-unit.source: This method must not return `null` because on deserialization the data will be cast to type <xref:System.Object> and an <xref:System.InvalidCastException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan ikke returnere `null` fordi på deserialisering dataene konverteres til typen <xref:System.Object>og en <xref:System.InvalidCastException>forårsakes.</xref:System.InvalidCastException> </xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: The object to substitute.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som skal erstatte.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that the substituted object should be assigned to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som erstattet objektet skal tilordnes.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The substituted object that will be serialized.
trans-unit.target: Virtuell objektet som skal serialiseres.

trans-unit.source: The object must be serializable by the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: Objektet må være serialiserbare av <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractSerializer>

trans-unit.source: For example, it must be marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute> attribute or other mechanisms that the serializer recognizes.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den må være merket med den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>attributt eller andre mekanismer serialiseringen gjenkjenner.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>

trans-unit.source: During schema import, returns the type referenced by the schema.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer typen referert til av skjemaet under skjemaimport.

trans-unit.source: `Null` should be returned if a CLR type does not exist for representing the schema type.
trans-unit.target: `Null`skal returneres hvis en CLR-typen ikke finnes for representasjon av skjematypen.

trans-unit.source: This will cause a new type to be generated during schema import.
trans-unit.target: Dette vil føre til en ny type genereres under skjemaimport.

trans-unit.source: The name of the type in schema.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på typen i skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: The namespace of the type in schema.
trans-unit.target: Navneområdet for typen i skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: The object that represents the annotation inserted into the XML schema definition, which is data that can be used for finding the referenced type.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som representerer merknaden satt inn i XML-skjemadefinisjon, som er data som kan brukes til å finne den refererte typen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> to use for the referenced type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>skal brukes for den refererte typen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Processes the type that has been generated from the imported schema.
trans-unit.target: Behandler typen som er generert fra importerte skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: The input <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration> or other information in the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit> can be modified by the user in this method.
trans-unit.target: Inndataene <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration>eller annen informasjon i den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit>kan endres av brukeren i denne metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration>

trans-unit.source: If `null` is returned, it will cause the type to not be generated.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `null` returneres den vil føre til at typen ikke genereres.

trans-unit.source: If a new <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration> is returned, it will replace the original type generated.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en ny <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration>returneres, vil det erstatte den opprinnelige typen som er generert.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration"></xref> to process that represents the type declaration generated during schema import.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration"> </xref> til prosess som representerer deklarasjon av typen generert under skjemaimport av.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"></xref> that contains the other code generated during schema import.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCompileUnit"> </xref> som inneholder koden generert under skjemaimport av.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration"></xref> that contains the processed type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeDeclaration"> </xref> som inneholder den behandlede typen.
